title: Various Artists - Beck Song Reader [2014] 320 kbps
description:
Song Reader was released as a book of sheet music by American alternative music artist Beck released on December 11, 2012. The book includes 20 songs worth of sheet music and more than 100 pages of art.

Now 20 different artists, including Jack White, Jarvis Cocker, Fun, father/son team Tweedy, Norah Jones, Laura Marling, Eleanor Friedberger, and even Jack Black have recorded this songs and release this as a collaborative album.
